    "beat": "Dusk over a windswept clifftop village that has feared the mountain for a hundred years. Elder Mara begs Jim to end the curse before the last seal breaks.",
    "narration": [
      "The wind off the sea carries the smell of woodsmoke and old secrets.",
      "Elder Mara spoke of a curse, but Illinois Jim only heard the call of adventure.",
      "The trail ahead is blocked by the old village gate. There must be a release lever nearby."
    ]
  },
